Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,connected to the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the captain was acting on his own,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}of Ichigo Kurosaki and the others?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.58,0:01:35.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo and his comrades enter\Nthe Soul Society in pursuit of Rurichiyo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.58,0:01:38.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and disrupt the marriage ceremony\Nbeing held in the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:40.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, they fall into Kumoi’s trap and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:44.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,end up surrounded by\NSoi Fon and Squad 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:49.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to find the real Rurichiyo\Nas soon as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.49,0:01:52.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo gets away from Soi Fon and\Nescapes into an underground passage,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:55.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but he is discovered by Squad 3 and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:57.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,gets into a fierce fight with Amagai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:02.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Shu Kannogi throws himself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:04.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,between them to stop the fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:07.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and upon learning of\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan’s dark secrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:10.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagai declares that he will support\NIchigo and his comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:14.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Move quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:28.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:29.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Omaeda!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:31.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:33.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The security group has been deployed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:34.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your next order?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Maintain present status.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:37.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:39.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides us and Squad 3,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:43.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,all squads have been marching\Naround since this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:46.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the Punishment Force\Nhas joined them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:49.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means there’s nothing else for us to do
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:51.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but to stay put for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:09.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If they were to harbor Kibune,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:11.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}this would be the most suspicious place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:14.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if the Court Guards keep\Ncoming and going,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the chances are low that he’d approach.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:19.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to search somewhere else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:29.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:32.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain and Ichigo Kurosaki have…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.37,0:03:35.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The possibility of a conspiracy\Ninside the Kasumiohji Clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So what’ll we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:41.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have several places in mind.\NWe’ll check those.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:43.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:46.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m helping you due to\Nmy personal feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:49.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot involve my squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So I sent them back to the barracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:55.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aida and a few others have agreed\Nto help out though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:04:01.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say… Why have you decided\Nto help us so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:04.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You may end up making enemies\Nof other Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:08.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I have some issues too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:11.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me your reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:13.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:16.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,First, let’s get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:18.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll explain while we move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:19.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:20.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We’d better report this\Nto Captain Komamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:34.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s a man named Kibune
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:40.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who is a Third Seat in my squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:42.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s extremely skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:44.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems he’s somehow \Nconnected to the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:50.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, it seems\Nhe’s hiding that connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:52.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Having ties under current circumstances is one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:55.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but he’s had connections long before\Nyou guys stirred up trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:59.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You think it’s connected to this incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:00.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:03.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,\NI’ve been having Kira watch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:06.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And now Kibune has been missing\Nsince this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:10.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is searching for\NKibune’s whereabouts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:12.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So that’s why he wasn’t around?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:15.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s difficult to suspect a comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:18.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then rather than coming with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:22.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,shouldn’t you report this to the higher-ups?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:25.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kibune is a man I chose personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:27.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If it’s proven that he’s been dishonest,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:29.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it’s my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:33.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens,\NI’ll deal with him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:35.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you should know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:38.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Thirteen Court Guard Squads\Nare very stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:41.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’ll take too long to\Nrun things by them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:43.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:48.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you had an idea about\Nwhere Ruricchi might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:54.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we’ll check out relevant areas\Ninside the Kasumiohji mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:06:00.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the end of\NCaptain Komamura’s message.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.62,0:06:03.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. You may go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:04.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:09.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Head Captain, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:11.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it known to all squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:15.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of Squad 3, Shusuke Amagai,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:18.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,is suspected of grave offenses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:20.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He is to be pursued immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:21.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:24.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am calling an emergency\NCaptains’ Meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:28.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagai did what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:29.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:33.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 7 members witnessed Amagai
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:35.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,collaborating with Ichigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:38.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. And that’s why\Nwe’re being called out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:40.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:42.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what’s happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.62,0:06:45.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? Just…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:50.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. We can’t avoid a disturbance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:56.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey guys! We’re the ones\Nwho first uncovered this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:58.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t lose to the other squads!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:00.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Right!\N– Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:04.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, it was around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:06.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Y-Yes, sir! That is correct!\N– Y-Yes, sir! That is correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:10.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But why Captain Amagai?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:17.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:19.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Abarai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:22.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can’t you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m looking for someone, just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:25.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:31.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But you’re awfully far from\Nyour assigned positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:34.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear your men were the first
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:36.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to find Ichigo and Captain Amagai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:40.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So it wouldn’t be strange if\Nthey were still in the area, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:43.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:47.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is our assigned section.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:50.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to your section, as ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:59.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you’re doing, Abarai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:02.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I said to go back. Can’t you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:03.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Iba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:06.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:09.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:15.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:17.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t give a damn about\Nsome Substitute Soul Reaper
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:19.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,or the new captain of Squad 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:22.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But if there’s gonna be a fight,\NSquad 11 will be there first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:25.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:31.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:34.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Hisagi of Squad 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:37.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Squad 9’s area.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to your barracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:42.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:44.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for a fight, sir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:46.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t order us around just
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:48.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,because you’re a lieutenant,\Nor we’ll get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:50.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t take us for fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:55.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a fool for trying to reason with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:58.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have used force from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:02.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s just fine with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:04.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:10.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll take you on, Hisagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:12.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Madarame!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:19.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know what\Nthis Captain Amagai is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:22.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But one thing is certain…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:27.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know Ichigo and Rukia better\Nthan anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:29.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So Iba, let me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:32.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want you guys to\Nget involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:36.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:40.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that Substitute Soul Reaper\Nvery well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:42.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this is an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:45.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot abandon my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:47.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So get rid of your\Nown personal feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:53.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and act as a lieutenant should!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:55.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can’t…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:10:00.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll have you leave,\Neven if I have to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:02.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:06.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you’d be\Na bit more understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:09.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If that’s what you say,\Nthen I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:14.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m passing through,\Neven if I have to use force!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:18.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:20.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:24.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:36.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:37.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:39.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No one’s seen anyone suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.92,0:10:40.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:42.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But there’s something even worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:44.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Word has already spread of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:47.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Amagai going with the Substitute Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:48.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:51.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inose, how did you talk to\Nthe head of security
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in this current situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:57.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to have concluded that the \Ncaptain was acting on his own,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:11:00.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so our squad isn’t under suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:01.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:03.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Amagai seemed to be
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:07.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,totally trusting of that Substitute Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:09.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he’ll be okay though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:14.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We can’t say anything certain about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:17.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now,\Nwe’ve left that sort of thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:19.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to Lieutenant Kira and Kibune.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:23.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which,\Nwhere’s Lieutenant Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:27.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s been out all morning,\Nacting on the captain’s orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:31.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Cripes. What’s going on anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:44.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it’s useless to\N search at random.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:48.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, why did Kibune choose\Nthis moment to go into hiding?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.26,0:11:52.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it connected with the appearance of \NIchigo Kurosaki and the others?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:54.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Or…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:02.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,\NI have to find Kibune quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could he have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:13.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it,\NI know so little about Kibune.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:18.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he was closer to Inose and Aida.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:23.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They used to talk about things\Nonly they would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew of its existence,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:36.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but this is the first time\NI’ve ever entered this place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:37.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Me too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:40.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, people don’t use\Nfighting arenas anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But since we have access to it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:46.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Kibune felt we could use it\Nfor our training drill.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.23,0:12:51.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A place to hide without\Nanyone noticing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:53.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:12:59.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:04.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In summary,\Ncapture Ichigo Kurosaki and Rukia Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:07.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And quickly restrain Captain Amagai
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:09.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who is suspected of aiding these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:11.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Head Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.53,0:13:14.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If I may say so,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:17.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Amagai’s actions are unclear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:19.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are also puzzling aspects
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:21.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,of the actions of Ichigo Kurosaki\Nand the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:24.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, what reason would
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:27.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,they have to infiltrate the Kasumiohji mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:31.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t believe they would act\Nwithout good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:35.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it’s necessary to\Ninvestigate the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:36.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:40.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I forbid any investigation\Ninto the Kasumiohji Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:44.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All squads! Carry out my orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:56.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t understand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:14:00.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The Kasumiohji Clan are\Nhigh-ranking aristocrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:03.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it’s probably safe to say they are at
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:05.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the root of this disturbance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:08.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you’re right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:10.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the chaos may
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:11.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,even spread to the Court Guard Squads!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:12.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:14.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:16.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s a squabble in the courtyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you’re so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:27.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Abarai, you haven’t changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.75,0:14:31.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Iba?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:35.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Orders, orders…\NAre orders that important?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That goes without saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:47.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Covering yourself is the one thing\Nyou’re good at, Hisagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:50.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Madarame… Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:54.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Split apart, Hozukimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:02.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren’t you going\Nto capture Ichigo, Hisagi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:03.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:18.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t give a damn, do you, Abarai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:22.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s because you’re in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:27.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what you’re doing\Nis disobeying orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:31.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I will stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:32.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:37.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Iba.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.61,0:15:42.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t understand why
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:44.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo and Rukia
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:47.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,would act so recklessly without a good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:52.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But Ichigo won’t stop until\Nhe gets his answers…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:54.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:01.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking, Madarame?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:04.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your squad and\Nreturn to your position!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:07.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Cripes. You’re so stubborn as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Think a little, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:15.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re on to something\Nwe haven’t noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:17.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why Ichigo and\Nthe others are taking action!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can’t you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:20.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:23.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s no reason for them\Nto disrupt the order!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:26.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve met him before, haven’t you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:28.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s got nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:31.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. That’s why you’re such a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:41.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Lieutenant Kira!\N– Lieutenant Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:42.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.24,0:16:46.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s Sugama, the one who’s been\Nmissing since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:50.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who went after\NThird Seat Kibune last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:54.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Amagai ordered us\Nto return to the barracks,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:56.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and the squadsman\Nwho stayed back found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:02.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can return to the barracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:03.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Huh?\N– Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:26.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:30.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything is worth trying after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:32.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It is just like Ichigo said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:36.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness,\Nno one seems to be around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:42.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems nothing ever goes\Nthe way you want it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:48.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who are they?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:50.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:53.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s Princess Rurichiyo\Nof the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:55.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:58.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’d better let Captain Amagai know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:06.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, the fact that the princess\Nof the Kasumiohji Clan is here…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:08.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That means…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:16.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:19.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You chose the wrong opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:28.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you will tell me what\Nyou’re doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:32.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:36.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the one who chose\Nthe wrong opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:37.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:49.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:04.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What’s with their power?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:07.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Their speed and Spiritual Pressure\Nrose suddenly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:09.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! I said to let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:14.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You are from\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:17.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Rurichiyo!\NYou are being insolent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:18.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Hold it!\N– Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:28.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:36.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:39.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:45.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In various places, Spiritual Pressure\Nis going every which way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:49.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All this chaos resulting from\Njust one order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:50.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is most unusual, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:53.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:56.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll prove their innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:00.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you’re going so far as to promise that…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:04.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then,\NI’ll believe in Ichigo Kurosaki too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:08.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not the only one.\NIt’s likely we all do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:12.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Most men have faith in that fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:16.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we have to carry out\Nour orders and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:19.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,find those two and Captain Amagai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:24.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to prove their innocence,\Nas you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:27.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cross swords with Ichigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:32.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you’ll understand why\Nhe’s raising hell like crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:35.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:40.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t let anyone get in his way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:43.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So what’ll you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:47.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And if they’re really doing\Nsomething wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll deal with it at that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:51.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will definitely…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:53.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– kill him!\N– kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Can I catch up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:29.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I must say, everything you do\Nis always too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:34.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The princess left long ago, Lieutenant Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:36.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:39.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything that’s happened is\Nyour doing…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.59,0:21:42.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Seat Kibune.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.44,0:23:24.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hisagi, you saw a lot of action today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.18,0:23:26.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was like this until recently
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.70,0:23:29.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,when Squad 3 started getting\Nall the attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:30.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:32.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’d better do my best here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.92,0:23:34.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s been bugging you, hasn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.45,0:23:37.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.24,0:23:39.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I’m hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.93,0:23:42.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go eat something?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.27,0:23:43.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.86,0:23:45.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll take you somewhere\Nyou can eat free, good food.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.61,0:23:47.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.27,0:23:51.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You came again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.90,0:23:53.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.15,0:23:54.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some leftovers from lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.98,0:23:55.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.26,0:23:57.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Leftovers?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.60,0:24:01.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But free, fancy foods…all you can eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.04,0:24:02.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:05.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you have any pride?